      "p1": "The Burger House Damauli wasn't born in a boardroom—it was forged during the 2020 Lockdown. While the world stopped, we started. We spent those quiet months perfecting the ultimate crunch, engineering a delivery-first model that brought comfort to homes when it was needed most.",
